The garlic? A buck
or sixty pesos.

331
00:20:52,527 --> 00:20:54,757
A buck, boss.
Interested?

332
00:20:56,927 --> 00:20:57,996
Music Man?

333
00:20:58,687 --> 00:21:00,564
A buck or sixty pesos.

334
00:21:00,727 --> 00:21:02,080
That's half my wage.

335
00:21:02,247 --> 00:21:04,158
