It's not too hard.

427
00:28:08,447 --> 00:28:09,675
I even earn more.

428
00:28:10,207 --> 00:28:10,923
Good.

429
00:28:13,087 --> 00:28:14,839
- Are you just out for a drive?
- No.

430
00:28:15,007 --> 00:28:18,761
