Look, here's the service order.

435
00:28:38,167 --> 00:28:41,557
I'm sorry, young man, but
we only take dollars here.

436
00:28:41,727 --> 00:28:44,161
Perhaps further on
they can help you.

437
00:28:45,007 --> 00:28:46,326
- Come on.
- Right.

