450
00:29:44,007 --> 00:29:46,237
- What subject?
- Economics.

451
00:29:48,327 --> 00:29:51,876
So she knows how to get
out of this mess, right?

452
00:29:53,247 --> 00:29:56,205
Socialist political economics
was what she taught me.

